    v0 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.96 / v2 + 0.54)) - ((v1 + 0.23 + v2 + 0.62) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.75)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.86)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos((tmp + 0.01 * v2 + 0.10)))
